  "description": "A wide-angle shot of the San Francisco skyline and the Bay Bridge on a clear, sunny day. The iconic Transamerica Pyramid is prominently featured amongst the city's modern skyscrapers. The Bay Bridge spans the bay with its distinctive suspension towers and cable system. Beneath the bridge, a lower level appears to be constructed with support structures. In the foreground, the blue waters of the bay exhibit gentle ripples. Beyond the city and bridge, rolling hills can be seen in the distance. The sky is a vibrant, cloudless blue.",
